<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l19">vvie Jm Eẏtell Goltſtein von <expan>Chuncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Ewterleins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l20"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> der hinter ew cʒum Rad ſicʒe entſagt hab / damit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l23">Er niht <expan>cʒuſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> hab <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_166_line_1576586732015_5819">mit </ab></add> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_166_r1l22">~ <expan>Ewt<ex>er</ex>lein</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l24"><expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet etc ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>p</expan></del> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l25"><expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan> poſt franciſci </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_166" id="82v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Göczen von <expan>Perlichinge<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Göcze, uns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie im Eytell Goltstein von
              <expan>Chuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Ewterleins <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, der hinter
            ew czum Rad sicze, entsagt hab, damit er niht <expan>czu schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> hab.
                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <add>mit</add> dem
              <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<add><expan>Ewt<ex>er</ex>lein</expan></add>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet etc. ut
                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan> post Francisci.</ab>
</div>
